/* 2011–present: Evolving programs */ Corrected both teams' 2017 records. Each was 4-6 coming into the matchup, not 4-7, as both teams had canceled/postponed games in September of that season due to Hurricane Irma. Florida finished 4-7 that season, while Florida State rescheduled their matchup against Louisiana-Lafayette to achieve bowl eligibility and finished 7-6.
